r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  say</a> around here is th=
at it is good for your career, in finance, to lose a billion dollars. Losin=
g a billion dollars indicates, to your next employer or investors, that som=
eone =E2=80=94=C2=A0presumably someone smart, who had a billion dollars =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0trusted you with a billion dollars. It shows that you had the a=
bility and nerve to take risks, which is (within reason) an attractive qual=
ity in high finance. And presumably you learned valuable lessons about what=
ever went wrong, and next time you will take=C2=A0<em>better=C2=A0</em>risk=
s and=C2=A0<em>make=C2=A0</em>a lot of money instead of losing it.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I think of this as applying mostly to traders =
at big banks and hedge funds, but it has broader applicability. Adam Neuman=
n incinerated truly titanic amounts of investor money at WeWork Inc., which=
 was bad, and got him removed as chief executive officer of WeWork. But it =
was also =E2=80=A6=C2=A0impressive? And so if you are an investor, and Adam=
 Neumann calls you and says =E2=80=9Chey can you put money into my new thin=
g,=E2=80=9D you might think thoughts like:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">I should take this meeting, it will b=
e funny.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Adam Neumann has experien=
ce running a very large fast-growing business. Into the ground, yes, but no=
t everyone has that experience.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Pr=
obably he learned some lessons and won=E2=80=99t incinerate=C2=A0<em>my=C2=
=A0</em>money.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also, the charm that Neumann used to raise mon=
ey last time might work on you this time, even though you know what happene=
d last time. And so in fact Neumann has done pretty well at <a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29730538.256530/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY=
mxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDgtMjIvbWVtZS1zdG9jay12YWNh=
